      483.1 MB         Feb 17 14:29  art/train-00010-of-00011.parquet
  
  # Tree view
  hf buckets list julien-c/my-training-bucket --tree -h -R
                          ├── art/
  423.6 MB  Feb 17 14:29  │   ├── train-00000-of-00011.parquet
